message: Any neat places open after midnight?
The Summit in the mission used to be open til 2 but they changed the hours to midnight as they were losing money staying open that late. It's a shame. :/
the Starbucks on California in Laurel Heights is open 24 hours
Yeah, I've heard some pretty good things about that Starbucks @athst
@athst - this place clears up nicely at about 3:00 am - before that it's a bit sloppy with people sleeping on their laptops
Does anyone know of good late night coffee shops in Russian Hill?
Sadly, all the coffee joints in Russian Hill close before 11pm.
